headline: Is O'Reilly Automotive Stock a Buy After Its 15-for-1 Stock Split?
summary: O'Reilly Automotive stock has consistently soared since its IPO.  Auto repairs are an essential need that car owners cannot forgo.  If you showed me a picture of O'Reilly Automotive's (NASDAQ: ORLY) stock performance since its initial public offering (IPO) in 1993, I would assume I was looking at a disruptive tech stock instead of an auto parts retailer.
